caption.title: Alignment of amino acid sequences of RVFV strain 35/74 and MP-12.
caption.p: Red boxes indicates amino acid differences. Green box epitope of mAb Gn32. Protein secondary structure (e.g. alpha helix, turns and beta strand) was predicted by EMBOSS 6.5.7 using the original Garnier Osguthorpe Robson algorithm (GOR I) provided by the EMBOSS suite ( http://emboss.sourceforge.net/).
